show.description: In a twist of fate, Su Yanran, betrayed by her family and desperate to save her ailing mother, crosses paths with wealthy heir Fu Hansheng, who, while investigating his nephew’s mysterious death, pretends to be her unwanted groom, leading to a journey of love and redemption.
